Full Description: In 2010, Zuujit LLC was formed to capitalize on the limitations, excessive costs and difficulties in conducting online sales through Amazon, Craigslist and eBay. Zuujit’s goal is to make it easy to buy, sell, share, and ship items online. Free listings, safe payments, and an integrated system that makes shipping easy are all designed with at ease of use and time conservation in mind. Zuujit merges the power of social networking with the advantages of e-commerce. The “Zuujit Social Marketplace” gives users the ability to price, buy, sell, share, and ship items using any web-enabled device. Zuujit doesn’t charge discouraging fees or promote third party advertising on the site. Sellers only pay a 2.8% credit card processing fee, and buyers receive from 10% to 33% off retail shipping rates. The company also offers cutting-edge fundraising software for charities, and has already attracted high-profile organizations such as Food Bank, Boy Scouts of America, YMCA, Habitat For Humanity, UnityShoppe, and the Not For Sale Campaign. The unique system gives these charities the ability to ask their supporters to donate items using Zuujit’s system. Zuujit processes the transactions and distributes funds from donated goods to the charity. Unlike any other competing programs, charities keep a minimum of 97% of the proceeds. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Santa Barbara, California.

Full Description: Archery N Motion is your gateway to an elevated shooting experience. Founded by Sam, a passionate hunter and competitive shooter, we bring innovation to the range. Our moving target platform offers realism, versatility, and precision. Sam's deep-rooted expertise in hunting and competitive shooting inspired the creation of a versatile platform. It caters to both archery and firearms enthusiasts, working seamlessly with various 3D archery target manufacturers, steel plates, and cardboard targets. One of our core missions is to improve accuracy through practice on moving targets. We understand that honing your skills with moving targets enhances your adaptability, precision, and overall proficiency. Whether you're preparing for a hunting season, a competitive event, or simply enjoying recreational shooting, our platform empowers you to become a more skilled and confident shooter. But our mission goes beyond just improving accuracy; it's also about reducing the number of wounded big game animals. By providing a realistic training environment, we help hunters make more humane and ethical shots, ensuring a cleaner harvest and minimizing the risk of injured wildlife. We believe in responsible hunting and the importance of respect and reverence for nature. Powered by a 12V system, our platform is efficient and user-friendly, ensuring quick and hassle-free setup. Join us on this journey of innovation and precision, and discover how Archery N Motion can enhance your shooting skills while contributing to a more responsible and ethical approach to hunting. Welcome to a new era of moving target excellence! Where every shot counts!
